r i kontakt med. Han vil fx gerne have ros af sin kreste, og han sger i det hele taget at give hendes ansvaret for hvordan han lever sit liv.</p>\n        <!-- Button -->\n        <div class=\"card-btn\"><a href=\"https://www.arnoldbusck.dk/boeger/krop-og-sind/naturens-muntre-soen?gclid=CjwKCAjw0N3nBRBvEiwAHMwvNhmKRAG_ROpRxCaXTZHB1Ap_93so6ppIfgL5RVkpQBbioW_ZxCCcSxoCrssQAvD_BwE\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Se mere</a></div>\n    \n      </div>\n    \n    </div>\n    <!-- Card -->\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    </section>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html /-->', 'parterapi-section-2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '56-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-10-02 13:44:55', '2019-10-02 13:44:55', '', 56, 'https://korsaa.dk/2019/10/02/56-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
