(627, 1, '2019-10-22 14:25:49', '2019-10-22 14:25:49', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Opinion I Washington Examiner den 17. april 2019.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.b.dk/kronikker/hvor-nazisterne-havde-gestapo-har-den-moderne-feminisme-metoo-bevaegelsen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">opinion piece published</a>&nbsp;over the weekend, Danish psychologist and therapist Finn Korsaa likened the #MeToo movement there with the Nazi Gestapo. Korsaa, a privately practicing psychologist, author, and regular columnist at the Danish daily Berlingske, said that the push for female equality has gone too far. That a columnist living in one of the most progressive parts of the world would say this speaks volumes for the trajectory of the #MeToo movement here in the United States.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Korsaa took issue with workplace gender quotas, pointing out the logical fallacies. \"The issue of women\'s quotas in corporate boards has long been like a hot potato. But how come no one insists on changing the significant overrepresentation of female psychologists? And why do we never ever hear demands for more men in the role of nurses?\" Korsaa wrote.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He then said he believes the origin of the current feminist offensive, which virtually demonizes all masculinity, stems from the way democracy ultimately overcame extreme patriarchal movements  Nazism and communism. Like a pendulum, ideological reactions have swung from one ideal to the other.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We have therefore come from one extreme to another. Where the Nazis had Gestapo and the communists had the KGB, modern feminism has its own home guard,\' in the form of the #MeToo movement and social justice warriors, who with their moral imperative seek to ensure that feminine values can maintain their monopoly through moral and political correctness, Korsaa explained.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Of course Korsaa would be intimately familiar with this concept of extreme equality, given his geographical location. The collectivist mentality rings loud and deep in Scandinavia and the surrounding regions, and is often rooted in Jante Law, originally coined by Aksel Sandemose. Jante Law boasts of a socialist-style Ten Commandments, like You\'re not to think&nbsp;<em>you</em>&nbsp;are more important than&nbsp;<em>we</em>&nbsp;are and You\'re not to think&nbsp;<em>you</em>&nbsp;are anything special.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Korsaa identified and even praised the polar opposite of this equality  which is found in traditional masculine values, which are now shunned. Channeling what seemed to be his own inner Dr. Jordan Peterson, Korsaa said masculine values--protection, hierarchy, sacrifice, and struggle  have value in society but are now met with contempt.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While it certainly doesnt seem like Americas #MeToo movement looks anything like a Gestapo  the Washington Post, the New Yorker, and the New York Times&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.pulitzer.org/prize-winners-by-year/2018\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">all won Pulitzers</a>&nbsp;Monday for shedding light on sexual assault and harassment  one can also easily see how the U.S. tends to follow suit with Scandinavia in many ways. If Korsaa is at all right, America should go forward with caution, apprehending sexual assault and identifying harassers, but without setting up its own home guard that demonizes and dismisses masculine values.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Nicole Russell is a contributor to the Washington Examiner\'s Beltway Confidential blog. She is a journalist in Washington, D.C., who previously worked in Republican politics in Minnesota. She was the 2010 recipient of the American Spectator\'s Young Journalist Award.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Danish psychologist compares #MeToo movement with Nazi Gestapo', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '624-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-10-22 14:25:49', '2019-10-22 14:25:49', '', 624, 'https://korsaa.dk/2019/10/22/624-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(628, 1, '2019-10-22 14:28:36', '2019-10-22 14:28:36', '<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"parterapiPage\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns parterapiPage\"><!-- wp:column {\"className\":\"parterapitext\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column parterapitext\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Parterapi</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"parterapi-text-head\"} -->\n<p class=\"parterapi-text-head\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<p class=\"parterapi-text-body\"><span>Parforholdet som livsopfyldelse er en drm, der rummer nsket om at dele tilvrelsens op og nedture. \nDen indeholder nsket om at gre den private historie til et led i en flles fortlling. Tidligere var personlig udvikling en forudstning for et gteskab, i vor tid er det undertiden omvendt. Derfor kan en skilsmisse vre en ndvendighed idet bruddet kan bruges som en trampolin for en psykologisk udvikling. \nEn skilsmisse kan dog ogs vre udslag af desperation, af kedsomhed eller tilbagevendende konflikter. Parterapi er i alle tilflde en mulighed for at afklare situationen og finde frem til en lsning.  \nDet kan vre svrt at leve i et uafklaret forhold, svrt hvis man gerne vil vre mand for sin kone, men ikke kan komme ud af rollen som bydreng. Svrt at leve i et forhold hvor begret er forsvundet. Den forelskede er ikke i tvivl om hvem, der er den vigtigste i livet. Hvis denne flelse forsvinder i gteskabet, er parterapi en mulighed.\n</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<p class=\"parterapi-text-head\">Parterapi<gwmw style=\"display:none;\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<p class=\"parterapi-text-body\">Parterapi kan vre en hjlp til at klargre problemstillingen og give en forstelse af hvad der kan gres for at tilvejebringe en nsket ndring. En parterapi tager sigte p hjlpe parterne til at fungere sammen p en mere givende og hensigtsmssig mde.<gwmw style=\"display:none;\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":99,\"className\":\"rounded-circle parterapiImage\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image rounded-circle parterapiImage\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/imgonline-com-ua-shape-SVxOrm8aWZ.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-99\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"parterapiPage\">\n    <div class=\"parterapitext\">\n    <p class=\"parterapi-text-head\">Skilsmisse</p>\n    <p class=\"parterapi-text-body\">Hvis uoverensstemmelserne ender i skilsmisse opstr der en rkke praktiske og flelsesmssige problemer som skal lses. Det kan vre sprgsmlet om, hvad man skal sige til brnene, og hvordan man fremover fr et forldreskab til at fungere uden at vre par. Dertil kommer skuffelserne og bitterheden over bruddet, og det er vigtigt at lre hvordan man kan bearbejde dem, uden at inddrage brnene.</p></div><div class=\"kontakt-div\"> <button class=\"kontakt-btn\">Kontakt mig</button></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<section class=\"section-feature\"><div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns parterapiPage\">\n    \n    <div class=\"wp-block-column sectionleft-img\">\n    <figure class=\"wp-block-image rounded-circle parterapiImage\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Vimmelskaftet-39-39a-c-41-41a-f-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-99\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\"></figure>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"wp-block-column parterapitext section_2\">\n    <h2>Psykoterapi</h2>\n    <p class=\"parterapi-text-body\"><span>Menneskets psyke er prget af omvltninger og kriser, der opstr og forlber med ndvendighed, ogs selv om man er vokset op i et trygt milj. Fra Homer til Mura-kami har digtere forsgt at skildre og fortolke disse indre konflikter, sammenbrud og jordrystelser. Dramaet i Odysseen svel som i Mordet p kommandanten, er forsg p at fortolke de psykologiske vilkr, som er menneskets evindelige mulighedsbetin-gelser og skbne. Den psykoterapi jeg tilbyder er en hjlp til at skabe orden i det indre kaos, i et forsg p at f magt over sig selv, og skabe mening og forstelse med tilvrelsen.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    </section>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<section class=\"section-nyste\">\n        <p class=\"section-nyste-head\">Finn Korsaas nyeste artikler:</p>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n         <div class=\"row\">\n           <div class=\"col-lg-4  col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12\">\n             <!-- Card -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n    \n      <!-- Card image -->\n      <img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"https://korsaa.dk/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/536478.jpg\" alt=\"Card image cap\">\n    \n      <!-- Card content -->\n      <div class=\"card-body\">\n    \n        <!-- Title -->\n        <h4 class=\"card-title\"><a>Flid er roden til al hslighed</a></h4>\n        <!-- Text -->\n        <p class=\"card-text\">Der er noget storartet over, at alle tiders kraftigste isbryder hedder Holger Danske. Den, og gipsfiguren af samme navn, der er placeret i Kronborgs klder, har det til flles, at de venter.</p>\n        <!-- Button -->\n        <a href=\"https://korsaa.dk/2019/09/04/flid-er-roden-til-al-haeslighed/\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Ls artikel</a>\n    \n      </div>\n    \n    </div>\n    <!-- Card -->\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12\">\n      <!-- Card -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n    \n      <!-- Card image -->\n      <img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"https://korsaa.dk/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/678345.jpg\" alt=\"Card image cap\">\n    \n      <!-- Card content -->\n      <div class=\"card-body\">\n    \n       <!-- Title -->\n        <h4 class=\"card-title\"><a>Danish psychologist compares #MeToo movement with Nazi Gestapo</a></h4>\n        <!-- Text -->\n        <p class=\"card-text\">In an opinion piece published over the weekend, Danish psychologist and therapist Finn Korsaa likened the #MeToo movement there with the Nazi Gestapo. Korsaa, a privately practicing psychologist, author, and regular columnist at the Danish daily Berlingske, said that the push for female equality has gone too far. </p>\n        <!-- Button -->\n        <div class=\"card-btn\"><a href=\"https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/opinion/danish-psychologist-compares-metoo-movement-with-nazi-gestapo\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Ls artikel</a></div>\n      </div>\n    \n    </div>\n    <!-- Card -->\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-lg-4  col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12\">\n      <!-- Card -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n    \n      <!-- Card image -->\n      <img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"https://korsaa.dk/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/678345.jpg\" alt=\"Card image cap\">\n    \n      <!-- Card content -->\n      <div class=\"card-body\">\n    \n        <!-- Title -->\n        <h4 class=\"card-title\"><a>Psykolog: Diagnoser er del af den mde, vi opfatter verden p</a></h4>\n        <!-- Text -->\n        <p class=\"card-text\">Nsten 70 procent af en lges patienter lider af noget, man kalder medicinsk uforklarlige sygdomme. Det betyder, at den praktiserende lge i 7 ud af 10 tilflde str over for noget, han ikke ved, hvad han skal stille op med, skriver Finn Korsaa.</p>\n        <!-- Button -->\n        <div class=\"card-btn\"><a href=\"https://korsaa.dk/2019/06/13/psykolog-diagnoser-er-del-af-den-made-vi-opfatter-verden-pa/?preview=true\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Ls artikel</a></div>\n    \n      </div>\n    \n    </div>\n    <!-- Card -->\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    </section>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<section class=\"section-mine\">\n        <div class=\"section-mine-head text-center\"><p><span class=\"section-mine-head-text\">Mine bog udgivelser</span></p></div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n     <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-sm-12 col-12 col-md-6 section-mine1\">\n         <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n    <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-6\">\n      <!-- Card image -->\n      <img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/0x500.png\" alt=\"Card image cap\">\n    </div>\n      <!-- Card content -->\n      <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-6 card-body\">\n    \n        <!-- Title -->\n        <h4 class=\"card-title\"><a>Ikke alle haner galer</a></h4>\n        <!-- Text -->\n        <p class=\"card-text\">Hje ambitioner uden tilsvarende karrieremuligheder skaber frustration. Sdan er det ogs med den moderne maskulinitet, der befinder sig mellem elskovskunst og inseminering. 1970ernes forsg p at ndre mandens natur har frt til store frustrationer - for kvinderne. Mnd har det tilsyneladende herligt som naturens muntre snner, men hvad med kvinderne? Og snnerne? Hvilke konsekvenser har det for den nye generation af drenge at se deres fdre indordne sig under et skrteregime? </p>\n        <!-- Button -->\n        <div class=\"card-btn\"><a href=\"https://www.saxo.com/dk/ikke-alle-haner-galer_finn-korsaafinn-korsaa_paperback_9788771707816\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Se mere</a></div>\n    \n      </div>\n    \n    </div>\n    <!-- Card -->\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-sm-12 col-12 col-md-6 section-mine2\">\n            <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n    <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-6\">\n      <!-- Card image -->\n      <img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/naturens-muntre-sn.jpg\" alt=\"Card image cap\">\n    </div>\n      <!-- Card content -->\n      <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-6 card-body\">\n    \n        <!-- Title -->\n        <h4 class=\"card-title\"><a>Naturens muntre sn</a></h4>\n        <!-- Text -->\n        <p class=\"card-text\">Bogen handler om mnd, der har en tilbjelighed til at forfre de kvinder han kommer i nrheden af ved at gre dem til mdre. Det kommer til udtryk i, at han sger bekrftelse af de kvinder han kommer i kontakt med. Han vil fx gerne have ros af sin kreste, og han sger i det hele taget at give hendes ansvaret for hvordan han lever sit liv.</p>\n        <!-- Button -->\n        <div class=\"card-btn\"><a href=\"https://www.arnoldbusck.dk/boeger/krop-og-sind/naturens-muntre-soen?gclid=CjwKCAjw0N3nBRBvEiwAHMwvNhmKRAG_ROpRxCaXTZHB1Ap_93so6ppIfgL5RVkpQBbioW_ZxCCcSxoCrssQAvD_BwE\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Se mere</a></div>\n    \n      </div>\n    \n    </div>\n    <!-- Card -->\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    </section>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html /-->', 'parterapi-section-2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '56-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-10-22 14:28:36', '2019-10-22 14:28:36', '', 56, 'https://korsaa.dk/2019/10/22/56-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
